'''辛克莱广播集团有限公司'''（{{lang-en|Sinclair Broadcast Group, Inc.}}，簡稱SBG）是一家由{{en-link|朱利安•辛克莱尔•史密斯|Julian Sinclair Smith}}家族控制的[[美国|美国]][[电信|电信]][[綜合企業|綜合企業]]以及美国第二大[[电视台|电视台]]运营商。它在[[美国|美国]]运营着193个电视台，覆盖40％的美国家庭。该公司旗下電視台製作的節目持[[美國保守主義|美國保守主義]]立場<ref name="wp-sinclairwjla">{{Cite web|title=Here's what happened the last time Sinclair bought a big-city station|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/heres-what-happened-the-last-time-sinclair-bought-a-big-city-station/2017/05/08/92433126-33f7-11e7-b4ee-434b6d506b37_story.html|accessdate=May 9, 2017|work=The Washington Post|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124230426/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/heres-what-happened-the-last-time-sinclair-bought-a-big-city-station/2017/05/08/92433126-33f7-11e7-b4ee-434b6d506b37_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nyt-foxrival">{{Cite news|title=Fox's Unfamiliar but Powerful Television Rival: Sinclair|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/03/business/dealbook/sinclair-media-expansion-fox-conservative-media.html|work=The New York Times|accessdate=May 9, 2017|first=Michael|author=de la Merced|first2=Nicholas|author2=Fandos|date=May 3, 2017|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418082644/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/03/business/dealbook/sinclair-media-expansion-fox-conservative-media.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bsun-antiwar">{{Cite web|title=Sinclair's TV program on Kerry is called illegal donation to Bush|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2004-10-12/news/0410120139_1_vietnam-war-stolen-honor-democratic-party/2|accessdate=May 9, 2017|work=Baltimore Sun|archive-date=2018-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725063437/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2004-10-12/news/0410120139_1_vietnam-war-stolen-honor-democratic-party/2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。公司总部位于[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴爾的摩|巴尔的摩]][[科基斯維爾_(馬里蘭州)|科基斯維爾]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hunt Valley|url=https://www.google.com/maps/place/Hunt+Vall